sampconfig is a script to enable PHP on HTTP server and run both HTTP and MYSQL server

SAMP = Slackware - Apache - Mysql - Php

==========================================================================
USAGE:

login as root &  copy sampconfig file to /usr/sbin and run `sampconfig` command as root.
==========================================================================


